      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.5646 - Ibn Mahbub narrated from Ali ibn Riʾab from Abu Ubaydah from Abu Jafar (as) who was asked about a paternal cousin and a grandfather (regarding inheritance).\nImam (as) said: \"The entire inheritance belongs to the grandfather.\""
        ]
